data.description: Beautiful home in the highly sought after community of Tortosa. The floorpan includes 3 beds, 2 full baths, large Great Room, neutral paint throughout and tons of windows make the home light and bright. The updated kitchen features SS appliances, granite countertops, a walk-in pantry, Breakfast room off the great room. The inviting Primary Bedroom has an en suite w/private toilet room, tub/shower combo, dual sinks & an updated walk-in closet. This home is equipped with an owned Solar System (2020) which has saved money towards the electric bill. HVAC system was replaced in 5/2020 with a Trane(2.5 ton). New appliances including W&D installed in 2017. New Microwave & WI-FI Garage Door opener in 2023, Primary Bath Tub was resurfaced in 1/2024, Newer Water Heater, Exterior painted in 2018.
